Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.01,0:00:03.99,Main Dialog,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,The festival was wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.99,0:00:07.04,Main Dialog,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Nishimi-san, I'd love to hear you play the piano again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:08.13,Main Dialog,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hear it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:09.27,Main Dialog,Girl 4,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a persimmon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:09.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:11.03,Main Dialog,Photography Club,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with the photography club!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:12.19,Main Dialog,Photography Club,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:14.09,Main Dialog,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,Stand next to each other, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:16.83,Main Dialog,Boy 1,0000,0000,0000,,This is the birth of the legendary duo of East High!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:18.79,Main Dialog,Photography Club,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stand closer to each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:20.74,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:21.95,Main Dialog,Photography Club,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:24.60,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when did you two become friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:26.72,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:28.97,Background Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How do you play in such perfect unison?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.92,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:31.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,When I count to five, run left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:31.47,Background Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to hide anything from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:33.47,Background Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:32.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,5...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:33.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,4...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:34.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,3...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:35.74,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,2...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:36.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:38.76,Main Dialog,Photography Club,0000,0000,0000,,They're escaping again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:39.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:44.48,Main Dialog,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, come on! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:48.99,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shit. The girls were supposed to be chasing after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:51.66,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, those guys are just like the Beatles!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.07,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I've learned from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:57.24,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about next year's festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:59.62,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking even further ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:01.20,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go so far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:03.89,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,that they'll never be able to catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:38.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:39.89,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I haven't been coming recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:42.26,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe in the basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:45.73,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:49.06,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon, would you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:52.23,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,check to see if Jun-nii's down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:54.10,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:56.98,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's not summer vacation, so why would Jun nii-san—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:00.72,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a lot's happened while you boys weren't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:03.99,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But he's not here now. He left last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:08.61,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I haven't seen you in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:09.62,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.38,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you, Prince Bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.57,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,My piano trio is finally together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:24.13,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi was disowned by his father right after he came back this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:25.79,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Disowned?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:28.97,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Well, first he went against his parents' wishes by going to college in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:31.96,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Then he stopped going to school
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:35.36,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,and got caught up in political activism instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:38.54,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,When the prodigal son wandered back home,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:41.28,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,it's no wonder his dad was furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.57,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi wasn't allowed to set foot in his family's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:49.74,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I ran into him at the bar not long after that, three sheets to the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:51.96,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,so I let him take refuge here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:53.71,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:57.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Is it my fault Jun-nii left?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.96,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.47,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,He happened to find a cheap room to rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.45,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:06.13,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:12.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Do not mope your life away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:20.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Playing one good session will drive away those blues, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:24.57,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Forget I did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:31.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, Bill Evans-dono, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.21,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:36.08,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we play a session so I can work off this gloominess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:46.60,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:50.98,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:56.34,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:58.98,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:10.91,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What made him change this much?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:14.04,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That one winter day in the basement...{\i0}{Ummm... I definitely don't remember this scene.... wtf?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:17.25,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(0,1000)}What was that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:21.05,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did he just do it on a whim?{\i0}
