Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:50.97,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or would he look at me again with those vacant eyes?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.49,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but that doesn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:07.55,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.47,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I got a soft spot for that angry face of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:14.38,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You had that same expression when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:15.48,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I remember it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.86,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:23.44,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Just go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:24.31,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:40.92,Main Dialog,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,Mukae-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:43.21,Main Dialog,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:45.92,Main Dialog,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,Would you give this to Nishimi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:50.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, wouldn't it be better if you gave it to him yoursel{\fsp7}f?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:52.05,Main Dialog,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.64,Main Dialog,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be too nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:54.74,Main Dialog,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,So please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:56.93,Background Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:00.94,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:05.69,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since the festival, but your popularity hasn't waned, Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:07.65,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.99,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I staring at?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.55,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I jealous?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.40,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has nothing to do with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:30.13,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:33.68,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, which scarf design do you think is better?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:38.73,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, lately there's this guy I kind of like,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:40.92,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm thinking about making one for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.25,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:44.15,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.40,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,But what about you, Ricchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.67,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there someone that you wanna knit for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.49,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's knit together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:56.10,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have anyone to give it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:59.39,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, be honest with yourself, Ricchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:03.10,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, you were staring at a certain someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.00,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.09,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:07.75,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:10.49,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-san is just a friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.34,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.70,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a beautiful color.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:22.73,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet Kaoru-san would look good in this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.65,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? Wait a second.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:31.67,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's wrong with me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:34.17,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is my heart beating so fast?{\i0}{because you are finally seeing our boys charm...damn harlot.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.41,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,That day?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:40.62,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:42.59,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I almost forgot about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:45.75,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna know why I did it?{use princess}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:50.19,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a little too stimulating for you, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:52.05,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.07,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I was just feeling kind of mischievous at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:08:59.43,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:01.94,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?{snap-raeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeep}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:04.19,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you come in here because you wanted me to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:06.35,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What were you hoping for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.44,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,A declaration of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:11.20,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disappoint you, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:13.45,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the kind of guy I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:19.74,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You've stopped fighting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:21.42,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Have you resigned to it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:22.62,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:26.87,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,"If I act like this, she'll probably run off."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:29.09,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you're thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:33.83,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.34,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,You can do what you want with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.03,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:45.78,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Go home and don't ever come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:48.76,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the same person I was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.06,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I dropped out of college
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:53.11,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,and got disowned from my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:58.07,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Society gave me the boot, and there's no way for me to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:02.08,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Get close to me, and your life will be ruined too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:05.64,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,If you understand what I'm sayin', get the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:18.72,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:22.13,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of you saying "Princess, Princess,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:25.48,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I'd get rid of the\N "princess" image you have of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:29.49,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not the same person you once were,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:34.20,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,then I can become a new person too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:42.49,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(0,250)}Katsuragi, I'm gonna become a new me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:43.94,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:50.29,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go throwing away
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:52.69,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,something precious for someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:05.13,Main Dialog,Arita,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the Katsuragi-kun I've heard so much about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:09.16,Main Dialog,Arita,0000,0000,0000,,How about saying something to mark the occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:10.02,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:13.83,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just passing through,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:18.77,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd like to share my opinion on what a college {\i1}should{\i0} be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:23.03,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuragi, you inspired me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:26.12,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Muroi, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.33,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,Listening to your speech
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:32.42,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,made me feel ashamed for doing nothing but study for exams and play music.
