Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.17,0:11:40.13,Main Dialog,Arita,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Katsuragi,
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.13,0:11:42.92,Main Dialog,Arita,0000,0000,0000,,in the next battle, if something were to happen to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:47.31,Main Dialog,Arita,0000,0000,0000,,would you take over, even just for a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:49.86,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Arita-san, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:57.90,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Muroi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:00.41,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Come over once in a while to play the sax.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:04.57,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:06.99,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,Arita-san's been arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:19.49,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,The bones are shattered,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:21.97,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,so the doc told me my fingers won't be able to move like they used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.96,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What about the sax?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:25.76,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't play anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:29.25,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look so glum, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:33.39,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can dump everything I don't need and just focus on the movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:37.22,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become a new me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:45.90,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:47.91,Main Dialog,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.95,Main Dialog,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:50.91,Main Dialog,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:12:59.71,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:04.72,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,...see any more people get hurt because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:11.22,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.81,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't intend to ask about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:18.19,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,But I can see that you're deeply hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:23.28,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Can't I support you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:27.53,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Am I being too pushy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:33.67,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:37.66,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pushy woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:56.52,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I better stop takin' naps on the roof.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:59.44,Main Dialog,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that was Yurika, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:01.89,Main Dialog,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,Was she called in by the teacher again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:05.03,Main Dialog,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Yurika's been acting weird these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.22,Main Dialog,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,She's totally changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:09.76,Main Dialog,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to that innocence she used to have?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:12.07,Main Dialog,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe something happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:14.79,Main Dialog,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,I asked her that, but she wouldn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:19.21,Main Dialog,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since she cut her hair like that, could it mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.41,Main Dialog,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,...a broken heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:24.59,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell happened?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.19,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did he do to her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.85,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're Sentaro, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:31.93,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like jazz?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:38.37,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ever since I first met Jun-nii, he's been like a big brother to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:41.36,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to get good at jazz like him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:42.94,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be strong like him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.86,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Become cool like him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:47.80,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I always trailed after Jun-nii,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:51.28,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}thinking I'd catch up someday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:52.86,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sen-bou...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:56.71,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Your woman forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:05.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Jun-nii would just talk to me, maybe I'd understand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:10.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if he did something to her,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:12.86,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.93,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jun-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:23.69,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.16,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:31.11,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,...bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:35.12,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:38.69,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one person I didn't want to find out about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:41.29,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,But what else could you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:44.64,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,He was bound to find out sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:52.11,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:54.81,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew she was beyond my reach from the start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:58.61,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew it. Or I thought I did, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:13.99,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't understand myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:17.59,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Definitely, when I'm with Kaoru-san,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:20.73,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can really feel at ease and have a good time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:26.21,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No. I decided long ago on the person that I like...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:29.96,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Ricchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:32.97,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Is Sen here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:35.71,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.64,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Knitting?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:41.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why would she bother hiding that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:03.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:08.28,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:13.32,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:16.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're obviously acting strangely today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.27,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:19.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I saw 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:21.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Saw who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:23.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,When I went to Jun-nii's apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:25.06,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,she was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:29.55,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're sure you saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:30.19,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:34.44,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,And of all people, it had to be Jun-nii.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That's what hurts the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:39.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:41.24,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothin' I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:45.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You've still got it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:50.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you were jilted, you've still got someone who cares for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:53.36,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's like they say. You can't see the forest for the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:58.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,And those trees are so tall, you must not be able to see a damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:02.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try looking more carefully?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:04.94,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it high time you realized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:06.56,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:09.56,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Figure it out for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:16.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I told him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:17.66,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:20.99,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You just got here, and you're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:23.55,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've got something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:26.08,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done knitting for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:30.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I couldn't help seeing it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:37.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan, you're blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Was I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:40.89,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:44.25,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a min...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure this is for the best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:54.02,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't have a relapse!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.53,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This doesn't hurt at all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:03.16,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:06.38,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You and this man from who knows where...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:10.08,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika, you're being tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:13.10,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:14.34,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:18.02,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring home a suitable partner for you before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:22.47,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So don't meet with this man again, Yurika. {So Yurika, don't meet with this man again.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:23.51,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:30.02,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika, your father is just talking to you like that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:32.20,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,because he's worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:38.03,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're a girl, so you have to take better care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:42.52,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case, keep next Saturday open, okay?
